* Action Items From **[notes]** → Extract tasks.
* Executive Summary Of **[paste text]** → Concise overview.
* Cover Letter For **[job description]** → Tailored cover letter.
* Resume Bullet For **[achievement]** → Strong resume bullet.
* LinkedIn Bio From **[details]** → Professional summary.
* Interview Questions For **[role]** → Prepare interview questions.
* Answer This Interview Question: **[question]** → Draft an excellent answer.
* Performance Review Phrases For **[trait]** → Useful review comments.

